# Lessons 5-7: Retrieval

<img src="https://images.code.org/ed33d52d1e8715c0cdc2e3ea53048e2d-Screenshot 2024-08-30 at 2.46.04 PM.png" alt="diagram showing the relationship between retrival and storage in generative AI" width="400px" style="border: 2px solid black; border-radius: 8px; float:right; margin: 0 0 40px 40px">


#### Lessons 5 through 7 help students develop an understanding of **retrieval**.

## Exploration
#### Students are guided through how **retrieval** can improve chatbot accuracy and relevance.

## Practice
#### Through examples and guided practice, students learn how retrieval can provide **current, specialized, and accurate information** to reduce AI hallucinations.

## Synthesis
#### Students brainstorm and plan strategies to achieve user goals, explore methods for testing and evaluating chatbots, and design chatbots tailored to each scenario, deciding between system prompts or retrieval.

